Fits in RxCrush Pill Crusher and other pill crushers that require a pouch. Can be used with 1ml, 3ml, 5ml ENFit syringes or larger. Smooth interior contours that restrict less medication delivering more accurate dose. Full Locking ENFit nozzle for more sure connection to syringe. Zip seal will not leak. RxCrush Pill Pouch with locking ENFit, ISO 80369-3 compliant. Use pouch to contain hazardous drugs to assist with USP<800>, USP<795>, and USP<797> compliance. ENFit tip fits to ENFit syringes. With transition connectors other style syringes can be attached. Syringe not included. See SYEN1-LDT, SYEN3-LDT, SYEN5 or SYEN10-2. Pouch cap not included. See CA02 or CA03. Thickness: 4 mil. Dimensions: 2\" x 4.375\" x 0.5\" each. 7\" x 9\" x 2\" for pack of 50. Optimal pill capacity is about 5, depending on the medication.\nInstructions for PP08 Pediatric Pill Pouch Insert pills into pouch to contain medication dust while crushing with RxCrush Pill Crusher. Connect pouch to a water-filled ENFit syringe. Do not inject water yet.
